{"tid":775478,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又有？統計學女碩士 轉投建造業！","createTime":"2018-08-11T07:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T06:59:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"89878409b27522f30eb5e7f43106fc23f6a83fea","tid":775478,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1737425/org/6cd23034155169b3b6d3ae7dedf1b492.jpg/aaFjJV2-805ptwlCZ_PPCYdQZVtmBTZVNQ-VXjUPlV4?v=w1440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1737425%2Forg%2F6cd23034155169b3b6d3ae7dedf1b492.jpg%2FaaFjJV2-805ptwlCZ_PPCYdQZVtmBTZVNQ-VXjUPlV4%3Fv%3Dw1440&d=GJcPMEruID2M0yd6UrIIRosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=a60445dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1737425/org/6cd23034155169b3b6d3ae7dedf1b492.jpg/aaFjJV2-805ptwlCZ_PPCYdQZVtmBTZVNQ-VXjUPlV4?v=w1440</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n胡善姮擁有亮眼的履歷，早年在英國修畢應用統計學碩士，做過零售業的行政管理，又曾和朋友集資開設補習社，問到為何突然轉行？胡善姮就認為興趣最重要，「我本身對手作及工藝有興趣，故選擇了香港建造學院的細木工藝課程，希望學一門手藝。」善姮更認為興趣是其習藝成績不斷進步的主因，對自己獲獎感到榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n作為女生，很難聯想到加入建造行業，善姮則認為細木工對體能要求相對較少，而且工藝講求精準、仔細，女生在這方面比男生有優勢。由零開始，在香港建造學院修讀「基本工藝課程」（現稱「建造證書課程」）「細木工藝科」，已畢業並工作將近一年，善姮正計劃參加學院的「進階工藝培訓計劃」，考取「大工牌」，長遠希望能創業承接工程。<br />\n<br />\n她寄語有意加入建造業的轉業人士，「不要讓經歷成為你的負擔，無論甚麼背景，只要有心，不論年齡也可從頭做起，甚至出人頭地！」<br />\n<br />\nmain pont:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">九月開課   把握申請機會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港建造學院開辦多項全日制課程，包括兩年制高等文憑、一年制建造文憑、一年制建造證書及短期課程，適合中學畢業生及轉業人士報讀。課程免學費，每月津貼由3,600元至10,200元不等，並設有就業輔導及工作轉介，就業率高達99%。有意申請人請把握九月開課前的良機，親臨九龍灣及上水院校即場報名面試，合資格者可即場獲取錄通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/221230/%E8%B5%B0%E5%87%BAcomfort-zone-%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E6%90%B5%E5%88%B0%E5%87%BA%E9%A0%AD%E5%A4%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F221230%2F%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%2587%25BAcomfort-zone-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2590%25B5%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A9&d=GJcPMEruID2M0yd6UrIIRosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3ef5dbc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/221230/%E8%B5%B0%E5%87%BAcomfort-zone-%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E6%90%B5%E5%88%B0%E5%87%BA%E9%A0%AD%E5%A4%A9</a>"},{"pid":"8d607ec0dc22700a13e3a946aea4a860bfa27788","tid":775478,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1736585/org/ad1b8a7d343109bfc9a519478a812dc6.jpg/4Xv2Cj5_Q5BJKAUFRWhkn48ety7JucaxdVcwHnVXMB4?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1736585%2Forg%2Fad1b8a7d343109bfc9a519478a812dc6.jpg%2F4Xv2Cj5_Q5BJKAUFRWhkn48ety7JucaxdVcwHnVXMB4%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=c0a7153d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61df677d7fa01695dd8d5b846e34be04a6ea6ea2","tid":775478,"uid":20867,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:13:42.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何<br />\n你的討論價值也必如何"},{"pid":"938322bf7f7f348548e78222366d8a10814cb947","tid":775478,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7997a21f156471dcda3196b4d49f3678f0b73a2c","tid":775478,"uid":118120,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"做媒姐<br />\n其實咪又係做管工, 科文果類唔洗自己郁手既"},{"pid":"8ce30b4be20bf9dcb07798358651e3779199faec","tid":775478,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:23:47.000Z","msg":"又多個<img src=\"/a